(Local) installation:
	make init
	make

(Production) installation:
	Change database settings
	Add Memcached
	Configure Lighttpd or the webserver of your choice to handle Django as fastcgi app

Dependencies (Yes, the -Z's at those easy_installs _are_ important.):
	Django
	python-docutils
	python-feedparser
	python-flup (For FastCGI support)
	django-grappelli (easy_install -Z django-grappelli)
	django-staticfiles (easy_install -Z django-staticfiles)

... More to follow
